PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 46 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding which occured in NOVA SCOTIA on or about September 23-24, 1999, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in that regard.
